text: Louise McKenzie (born 31 March 1964) is a British cross-country skier. She competed in three events at the 1988 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:British female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Great Britain Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1988 Winter Olympics Category:People from Badenoch and Strathspey
